fr.sorbonne_u.components.hem2023e3.equipments.heater

Class HeaterUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
      • fr.sorbonne_u.components.hem2023e3.equipments.heater.HeaterUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI, HeaterPushImplementationI

    public class HeaterUser
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
implements HeaterPushImplementationI
    The class HeaterTester implements a component performing tests for the class Heater as a BCM component.

    Description

    In unit test runs, the component performs a series of tests on the heater component. In integration test and SIL simulation runs, it simply switch on and off the heater, leaving to the other components (the heater controller and the HEM) the responsibility to test the heater component services and internal behaviour.

    Invariant

     invariant       true        // no invariant

    Created on : 2021-09-13

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
